example:
class Base:
    __slots__ = ("a", "b")


class Subclass(Base):
    __slots__ = ("a", "d")  # slot "a" redefined



Use instead:


class Base:
    __slots__ = ("a", "b")


class Subclass(Base):
    __slots__ = "d"

